This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with probabilistic models of sentences and language modeling. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it introduces a new type of recurrent neural network model. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with natural language processing and inference. The paper also mentions experiments involving image captioning, which could place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural networks.
